#Block:Human-Xenomorph Hybrid
# Ability Name							Description
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Acid Blood.MOD			DESC:Whenever a physical attack hurts a Hybrid, there is a chance for acid blood to do 'splash damage'. The DC for the Reflex save (anyone within 5 feet of the Hybrid) is equal to the damage made (divide by ? if it's a bludgeoning or piercing weapon). Damage from acid damage is 1d6 per 6 points made (round down), to a maximum of 10d6. Any item exposed to the spray must make a save vs. the DC of the amount of damage made (Mastercraft items get a +5 to the save). Failure destroys the item.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Unusual Physiology.MOD		DESC:Attempts to use Treat Injury on the Hybrid have a -4 penalty (unless they have the Xenomedic Feat). In addition, all items used must be custom-made to withstand the acidic blood.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Xeno-Sense.MOD			DESC:Whenever a Hybrid is within a mile of a Xenomorph, they may make a Wisdom check (DC 35-1 per Xenomorph within that range). If this succeeds, the Hybrid is aware of its presence, but gain no extra details of its location beyond a generic direction and range ('It's that way, near/far').
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Ignored Target.MOD		DESC:A Xenomorph will ignore a Hybrid until the Hybrid attacks it.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Impregnation Immunity.MOD	DESC:Hybrids cannot be infested by Xenomorphs.


#Block:Gallifreyians
CATEGORY=Special Ability|LowLight Vision.MOD		DESC:A Gallifreyan has low-light vision and can see objects twice as far away as a basic human. The effective radius of bright light or shadowy illumination is doubled.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Respiratory Bypass.MOD		DESC:A Gallifreyan can close down his respiratory system for a number of rounds equal to his Constitution x 3. This can be used to hold the effects of smoke and gas at bay.
#CATEGORY=Special Ability|Scent.MOD				DESC:This ability allows the Gallifreyan to detect approaching enemies, sniff out hidden foes and track by sense of smell.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Weakness to Gas Attacks.MOD	DESC:If a Gallifreyan fails to activate his Respiratory Bypass their enhanced sense of smell causes them to take a -4 penalty on Fortitude Saves to resist gas attacks. Corrosive gases inflict double damage.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Lindal Gland.MOD			DESC:A biological implant which triggers the process of regeneration when a Gallifreyan's hit points fall below 0. This process can be activated a maximum of 12 times.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Telepathy ~ Time Lord.MOD	DESC:Any Gallifreyan with an Intelligence of 6 or higher can communicate telepathically with any creature within 100 feet that has a language.

