#Magical Girl
Guardian Beast											CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			BENEFIT:A Mahou Shoujo has a magical creature that serves as her assistant and mentor. This Guardian Beast' takes the form of an animal of Tiny size or smaller, for example: Cat, Bat, Hawk, Lizard, Monkey, Owl, Rat, Raven, Snake (Tiny viper), Toad or Weasel. The Guardian Beast' has the ability scores of an animal of it's type with a +10 to Int and a +5 to Cha. In addition to it's special qualities and racial skill bonuses, the Guardian Beast' has the ability to speak. The Guardian Beast' is otherwise treated like a 1st-Level character in one of the basic classes. For each additional level the Mahou Shoujo obtain in this class, the Guardian Beast' obtains a level in a basic class.
Energy Attack											CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			BENEFIT:At 2nd Level, the Mahou Shoujo learns how to channel her inner power into an energy-based attack, dealing 2d6 points of damage. The player must decide whether this is expressed as a melee or ranged attack. If it is a melee attack, any Str-based bonus to damage applies. If it is a ranged attack, it has a range increment of 80 and a rate of fire of 1. In both instances, the attack threatens a critical on a roll of 20, for x2 damage. The player also decides what type of energy the weapon is expressed as. It can be Acid, Cold, Electricity, Fire, Sonic/Concussion, Positive or Negative energy-based (these latter two only affect Evil or Good supernaturals). At 7th-Level, the damage caused by the Mahou Shoujo's energy attack increases to 4d6. She also gains a secondary attack form, different in delivery and (or) energy type.
Spring Heeled											CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			BENEFIT:At 4th Level, the Mahou Shoujo gains a tremendous leaping ability. For the purpose of using the Jump skill, the Mahou Shoujo is treated as having twice her normal movement rate and having one size larger.
Invigorate												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			BENEFIT:At 5th Level, the Mahou Shoujo may, once per day, spend 1 action point in order to recover lost hit points. The number of lost hit points recovered is determined by rolling 1d6 per Mahou Shoujo level, restoring up to the character's total. At 8th Level, the Mahou Shoujo may, once per day, spend 1 action point in order to heal the hit point damage of another character. The number of hit points recovered is determined by rolling 1d6 per two Mahou Shoujo levels, restoring up the character's total. The Mahou Shoujo may not Invigorate herself and another person on the same day.
Fly													CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality			BENEFIT:At 10th Level, the Mahou Shoujo may spend 1 action point to fly for 10 minutes. She can fly at a speed of 60 feet (40 feet of carrying a medium or heavy load), ascends at half speed and descends at double speed, and her maneuverability is Good. If flight is not maintained by spending an additional action point, the character will begin to descend as if she were under the Feather Fall' spell.



